hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n住silom road 應該幾近bts站<br />\n我地都有講過儘量唔的士 都想搭下人地既公共交通<br />\n最驚係語言不通 因為聽講英文都唔係個個聽得明<br />\n不過我諗住都係旅遊區應該ok掛<br />\n唔該哂巴打先 我都冇諗過可以uber<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 旅行去多數都坐BTS或者MRT架啦<br />\n頂多坐下「篤篤」⋯<br />\n不過提提你，坐「篤篤」記得問左價先<br />\n不過你預佢開價實開3倍或以上⋯<br />\n你點同佢講價佢都實開大你既<br />\n你覺得價錢ok既先坐啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n語言不通就一半一半啦<br />\n有部分就真係完全唔知你講咩<br />\n有部分都叫還可以<br />\n不過遊客區既話都可以既⋯<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有咩隨便問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：老婆係當地泰國人，本人經常來回港泰兩地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b1c66c57b50676479d9768f01ea331eafe25429","tid":58053,"uid":8014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T02:42:25.000Z","msg":"搭單問下 夜晚11點幾落bkk 機場 搭uber 番酒店是否明智？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6e4ecb59985842f91043b5d5aa984ad0483c541","tid":58053,"uid":35969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T06:48:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>同男朋友兩個1月頭去曼谷<br />\n但兩個都未去過<br />\n想問下有冇啲咩地方係一定要去？<br />\n唔該哂大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nhea hea地 jj market都行到成日</blockquote><br />\n預左一日行jj market 唔該哂你先！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3505b730ee0671d10a31170e1d2e1f6f42a189e6","tid":58053,"uid":35969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T06:49:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>叫雞囉伸手黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n自己都有睇行程 係驚有啲咩地方必去我又唔知啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b32f83c8a2888ed5b72aea5856d657427cfd86c","tid":58053,"uid":35969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T06:52:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 旅行去多數都坐BTS或者MRT架啦<br />\n頂多坐下「篤篤」⋯<br />\n不過提提你，坐「篤篤」記得問左價先<br />\n不過你預佢開價實開3倍或以上⋯<br />\n你點同佢講價佢都實開大你既<br />\n你覺得價錢ok既先坐啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n語言不通就一半一半啦<br />\n有部分就真係完全唔知你講咩<br />\n有部分都叫還可以<br />\n不過遊客區既話都可以既⋯<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有咩隨便問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：老婆係當地泰國人，本人經常來回港泰兩地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n想問夜市！有冇邊個推介 唔該哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f577eac19c6afd0ec40ffe37e59344dbf74dfaa","tid":58053,"uid":11418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T13:40:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搭單問下 夜晚11點幾落bkk 機場 搭uber 番酒店是否明智？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實無所謂，最驚無車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有時坐的士仲好<br />\n機場的士站同香港一樣有飛仔比你，有埋車牌號，放心又安全！<br />\n<br />\n（泰國既係你要排隊禁機出飛仔再係番指定路口等的士黎）"},{"pid":"3d38089df0f68685a164526832e2721b94bee176","tid":58053,"uid":11418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T13:41:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 旅行去多數都坐BTS或者MRT架啦<br />\n頂多坐下「篤篤」⋯<br />\n不過提提你，坐「篤篤」記得問左價先<br />\n不過你預佢開價實開3倍或以上⋯<br />\n你點同佢講價佢都實開大你既<br />\n你覺得價錢ok既先坐啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n語言不通就一半一半啦<br />\n有部分就真係完全唔知你講咩<br />\n有部分都叫還可以<br />\n不過遊客區既話都可以既⋯<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有咩隨便問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：老婆係當地泰國人，本人經常來回港泰兩地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n想問夜市！有冇邊個推介 唔該哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n旅行去既都係火車夜市架啦！<br />\n我同老婆去開當地人d夜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n介紹唔到"},{"pid":"d6c1fda9dd0acafbf26b2e1fe2715df21f7fda99","tid":58053,"uid":17531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-04T01:12:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}